        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[gRPC Component now in github repo.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="grpc-component-now-in-github-repo">gRPC Component now in github repo.<a href="https://beauty-framework.github.io/blog/grpc-component-now-in-beta#grpc-component-now-in-github-repo" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to gRPC Component now in github repo." title="Direct link to gRPC Component now in github repo.">​</a></h3>
<p>Use it!</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">make</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">composer</span><span class="token plain"> require beauty-framework/grpc</span><br></span></code></pre></div></div>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">make</span><span class="token plain"> beauty grpc:install</span><br></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p>Full instruction in github repositoru.</p>
<p>Github repo: <a href="https://github.com/beauty-framework/grpc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/beauty-framework/grpc</a></p>
<p>Example app: <a href="https://github.com/beauty-framework/example-grpc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/beauty-framework/example-grpc</a></p>]]></content>
